            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

        <div class="container-fluid gedf-wrapper">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="h5">@@LeeCross</div>
                            <div class="h7 text-muted">Fullname : Miracles Lee Cross</div>
                            <div class="h7">
                                Developer of web applications, JavaScript, PHP, Java, Python, Ruby, Java, Node.js,
